main event: Report of Flying Saucer observed on April 27, 1953, by the 1st Fighter Group at March Air Force Base.
interesting points: The report requests conclusions of the UFO investigation be forwarded promptly., The document was part of Project Blue Book, an investigation program of the U.S. Air Force., The object sighted was described as saucer-shaped., The incident involved multiple communications documenting UFO sightings., No photographs were included or identified in the report.
witness description: Major D. McCamey, Captain USAF, 1st Fighter Group
